Postage $aver for Parcels is low-cost software that makes it easy to prepare your shipments for low USPS bulk parcel postage rates! 
Postage $aver for Parcels:
- prints USPS-certified tracking labels; 
- sorts your addresses by sack for quick preparation of your shipment; 
- prints required postage statement and reports;
- prints barcoded sack tags;
- prints easy-to-follow sacking instructions for each shipment; and, 
- uploads the required tracking file to USPS.

